title: Pirate Poppers
description:
Pirate Poppers game description

Climb aboard for some swashbucklin' pirate popping fun! Aim your cannonballs to clear away menacing chains and unlock trinkets and jewels that rain down from above. Begin as a lowly Landlubber and plunder your way up the ranks! Do you have what it takes to become a Living Legend? Do not miss this excellent game Pirate Poppers.
